org.apache.drill.test

Class ProfileParser.OperatorSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.ProfileParser.OperatorSummary
  • Enclosing class:
    ProfileParser

    public static class ProfileParser.OperatorSummary
extends Object
    Information about an operator definition: the plan-time information that appears in the plan portion of the profile. Also holds the "actuals" from the minor fragment portion of the profile. Allows integrating the "planned" vs. "actual" performance of the query.

    There is one operator definition (represented here), each of which may give rise to multiple operator executions (housed in minor fragments.) The opExecs field provides the list of operator executions (which provides access to operator metrics.)
